channel.title: Error with AutoSpawn
channel.description:
Well, I'm working on a minigame for my server and for some reason when I added two new NPC's and ran the server I got the following error:
[code]Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "1 710 " at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at NPCHandler.loadAutoSpawn(NPCHandler.java:1358) at NPCHandler.<init>(NPCHandler.java:23) at server.main(server.java:27) Starting GangScape v2 Server on 0.0.0.0:43594 [/code]
Thank you.
